---
<BaseLayout
  title="Does GDPR Apply to US Companies? Plain-English Guide for 2026 | PrivacyComply"
  description="Yes, GDPR applies to US companies with EU visitors — regardless of where you are based. Learn what you need to do, what fines look like, and how to get compliant fast."
  canonical="/gdpr-for-us-companies.html"
  ogType="article"
>
  <Fragment slot="schema">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(breadcrumbSchema)} />
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(articleSchema)} />
